            <div class="step-card"><div class="step-content"><span class="step-badge">Step 1-2</span><h3 class="step-title">Assessment + CTC Design</h3><p class="step-description">Review company type, employee categories, CTC structures, ESOP plan, freelancer terms, NCR presence. Design CTC with 50% basic, HRA Delhi rate, flexible benefits, variable pay documentation. ESOP exercise workflow mapped. Freelancer rate cards documented.</p><div class="step-highlights"><span class="highlight-tag"><svg viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2"><polyline points="20 6 9 17 4 12"/></svg>Assessed</span><span class="highlight-tag"><svg viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2"><polyline points="20 6 9 17 4 12"/></svg>CTC designed</span></div></div><div class="step-visual"><div class="step-illustration"><div class="illustration-icon"><svg viewBox="0 0 120 100" fill="none" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg"><rect x="15" y="5" width="90" height="70" rx="6" fill="#F0F4F8" stroke="#14365F" stroke-width="1.5"/><text x="60" y="40" font-size="7" fill="#E8712C" font-weight="800" text-anchor="middle" font-family="Arial">CTC</text></svg></div><span class="illustration-label">Designed</span><span class="step-number-large">01</span></div></div></div><div class="step-card"><div class="step-content"><span class="step-badge">Step 3-4</span><h3 class="step-title">Register + Monthly Payroll</h3><p class="step-description">PF/ESI registration. HRMS integrated. Monthly: fixed CTC + variable (if declared) + ESOP perquisite (if exercise) → TDS computed per employee. Freelancer S.194J processed alongside. PF/ESI by 15th. TDS by 7th. Payslips distributed.</p><div class="step-highlights"><span class="highlight-tag"><svg viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2"><polyline points="20 6 9 17 4 12"/></svg>Running</span><span class="highlight-tag"><svg viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2"><polyline points="20 6 9 17 4 12"/></svg>ESOP integrated</span></div></div><div class="step-visual"><div class="step-illustration"><div class="illustration-icon"><svg viewBox="0 0 120 100" fill="none" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg"><rect x="20" y="15" width="80" height="50" rx="6" fill="#F0F4F8" stroke="#14365F" stroke-width="1.5"/><text x="60" y="40" font-size="7" fill="#14365F" font-weight="700" text-anchor="middle" font-family="Arial">TDS</text></svg></div><span class="illustration-label">Computed</span><span class="step-number-large">02</span></div></div></div><div class="step-card"><div class="step-content"><span class="step-badge">Step 5-6</span><h3 class="step-title">Quarterly/Annual + Year-End</h3><p class="step-description">Form 24Q quarterly. Variable pay true-up after performance reviews. Increment cycle processing. ESOP vesting tracking. Freelancer Form 16A. Year-end: Form 16, PF/ESI annual, gratuity actuarial, department/project-wise payroll MIS.</p><div class="step-highlights"><span class="highlight-tag"><svg viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2"><polyline points="20 6 9 17 4 12"/></svg>All filed</span><span class="highlight-tag"><svg viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2"><polyline points="20 6 9 17 4 12"/></svg>MIS ready</span></div></div><div class="step-visual"><div class="step-illustration"><div class="illustration-icon"><svg viewBox="0 0 120 100" fill="none" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg"><rect x="20" y="10" width="80" height="60" rx="8" fill="#E8F5E9" stroke="#25D366" stroke-width="2"/><path d="M52 40l5 5 12-12" stroke="#25D366" stroke-width="3" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"/></svg></div><span class="illustration-label">Complete</span><span class="step-number-large">03</span></div></div></div>

